{"tid":2061200,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"公投延期620 無懼打壓決心不減 #二百萬三罷聯合陣線","createTime":"2020-06-12T08:15:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-17T11:26:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"05d59ce018cb7da7a200e91aec8a674af5323ecd","tid":2061200,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-12T08:15:37.000Z","msg":"‼️公投延期620 無懼打壓決心不減‼️ #二百萬三罷聯合陣線<br />\n20200612<br />\n<br />\nSource<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pg/283strike/posts/?ref=page_internal&amp;mt_nav=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpg%2F283strike%2Fposts%2F%3Fref%3Dpage_internal%26mt_nav%3D0&d=q8peb0UcLz3Z6%2FQAtnUTjMwxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=4a00bb78\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/pg/283strike/posts/?ref=page_internal&amp;mt_nav=0</a><br />\n<br />\n二百萬三罷聯合陣線<br />\n<br />\n‼️公投延期620 無懼打壓決心不減‼️<br />\n<br />\n天文臺話星期日有熱帶氣旋逼近並且會有狂風暴雨，經過商討之後，我哋決定將罷工罷課公投延期至<span style=\"color: orange;\">6月20日（下星期六）</span>，但絕對絕對唔會取消。<br />\n<br />\n今日兩辦同政府以致黨媒都一齊出聲批評罷工罷課公投，更加證明中共對公投非常關注，我哋一定要更多人參與，展現決心！大家記住投票表達意見以及參與工會活動都係我哋嘅基本權利，我哋唔會因爲咁而退縮！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">聽日嘅聯合招募都會照常</span>，只係星期日嘅公投延期。都係個句，<span style=\"color: orange;\">未入會嘅快啲入，唔好做deadline fighter啊！</span><br />\n<br />\n📌參與公投工會名單，公投前搵返所屬工會加入（名單陸續更新）<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/305DVqj\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F305DVqj&d=q8peb0UcLz3Z6%2FQAtnUTjMwxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=c51184e6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/305DVqj</a><br />\n<br />\n📌義工招募：<a href=\"https://forms.gle/c57jXxVZCpVYzofn7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2Fc57jXxVZCpVYzofn7&d=q8peb0UcLz3Z6%2FQAtnUTjMwxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=1975b931\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/c57jXxVZCpVYzofn7</a><br />\n<br />\n#向國安法說不<br />\n#積極備戰聯合罷工<br />\n#全民公投<br />\n----<br />\n🔴二百萬三罷聯合陣線🔴<br />\n抗爭 | 工會 | 罷工 | 行業行動<br />\n頻道 <a href=\"https://t.me/h